sources.title: Suteneko Tora-chan (1947)
sources.description: A mother cat and her kittens were taking a walk when they came upon a hungry Tora-chan. Giving the kittens their lunch which consisted of milk, she took the remainder of the milk and fed Tora-chan. The mother cat brings Tora-chan home with her family and all seemed to get along with him, except for the youngest kitten daughter.
